'''科里·斯科特·加德納'''（{{lang-en|'''Cory Scott Gardner'''}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.legistorm.com/memberbio/2735/Rep_Cory_Gardner_CO.html |title=Representative Cory Scott Gardner (Cory) (R-Colorado, 4th) – Biography from |publisher=LegiStorm |date= |accessdate=14 June 2011 |archive-date=2011-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110816003015/http://www.legistorm.com/memberbio/2735/Rep_Cory_Gardner_CO.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；{{bd|1974年|8月22日||}}），是一位美國[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]][[政治人物|政治人物]]，曾任[[科羅拉多州|科羅拉多州]][[美國參議院|美國參議院議員]]、科羅拉多州[[美國眾議院|美國眾議院議員]]及[[科羅拉多州眾議院|科羅拉多州眾議院]]議員。

加德納在2014年3月宣布競逐美國參議院議員席位，並迅速通過共和黨初選<ref>{{cite web|url=http://thehill.com/blogs/ballot-box/201036-gardners-final-primary-foe-drops-bid-in-colorado/|title=Gardner gets clear primary path in Colorado|date=18 March 2014|accessdate=18 March 2014|archive-date=2015-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150810162801/http://thehill.com/blogs/ballot-box/201036-gardners-final-primary-foe-drops-bid-in-colorado|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在{{le|2014年科羅拉多州美國參議院議員選舉|United States Senate election in Colorado, 2014|11月的選舉}}中擊敗前任[[民主黨_(美國)|民主黨]]籍參議員[[馬克·尤德爾|馬克·尤德爾]]當選該州參議員<ref name="abc.results">{{Cite news|url = http://abc30.com/news/republicans-up-5-seats-in-race-to-control-senate/380215/|title = REPUBLICANS UP 5 SEATS IN RACE TO CONTROL SENATE|last = |first = |date = |work = |accessdate = |archive-date = 2015-07-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150713181129/http://abc30.com/news/republicans-up-5-seats-in-race-to-control-senate/380215/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

